    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-8010-91a0-e5056dd53583",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "This is nastro , showcasing what can u do to your notion pages with ",
            "href": null
          },
          { "text": "nastro", "href": "http://nastro.xyz/" },
          { "text": ". so seat back , relax ,and chill. ", "href": null }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-809c-b97c-ee94b10b2a93",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "Thing u can do with nastro , customize theme , literally u can customize everything in nastro , from background colors , notion button color to text selection.",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-80ef-a5dd-c1b1c81efac5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "U can do seo , that for free , yes this is not a bait , notion charges for it , but with nastro u can do it easily and u can also add google analytics that is also free. ",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-80a3-a25b-c2375331f499",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "Nastro , provide some custom themes , and  templates .",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-8096-b885-c308f655f219",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "content": {
        "level": 2,
        "text": [{ "text": "why nastro exist ?", "href": null }]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-80be-bac7-d689693e92ac",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "nastro help you to represent notion’s pages truly yours ,",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-80ba-a21a-d91cffab78a4",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [{ "text": "you can add your own taste to it.", "href": null }]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-80a0-ba87-cf82f23d0c8b",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "nastro can help to make your fist website , that represent truly you , ",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-8078-a938-e286bb0b5a28",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "it can help you to publish blog on your name , (eliza.nastro.xyz)",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-806b-8a1b-fa3e8766edbc",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "it can help you to validate your idea without wasting thousands on just validations. (you can literally make small ecommerce website.",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
    {
      "id": "34185bde-2593-8004-aa09-fd8a7f48d15d",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "content": {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "it can help you to customize your notion journal ,which feels  good to you.",
            "href": null
          }
        ]
      },
      "hasChildren": false
    },
